## 5. User experience

### 5.1 Entry points & first-time user flow

- **Landing page**: Product overview, features, pricing tiers, CTA ("Start Free")
- **Registration**: Email-based sign-up, no credit card required for free tier
- **Onboarding**: 2-minute walkthrough (strategy creation, backtesting, deployment)
- **Broker connection**: Guided modal with Angel One or Zerodha setup steps
- **First strategy**: Template-based creation (select strategy type, fill parameters)
- **First backtest**: Run backtest, view results with metrics explanation
- **First trade**: Deploy to paper trading (no real money), view live dashboard

### 5.2 Core experience

- **Strategy Creation**: Simple no-code form, saves instantly, no deployment needed
  - Ensures traders can experiment quickly without technical barriers
  
- **Backtesting**: One-click run, async processing, email notification on completion
  - Removes waiting friction, lets traders continue working while backtest runs
  
- **Live Dashboard**: Real-time position updates every 5 seconds, large P&L display, quick action buttons
  - Traders see exactly what's happening without confusion or delay
  
- **Alerts**: Multi-channel (email, in-app, SMS future) with clear, actionable messages
  - Traders never miss important events (trade executed, SL hit, risk limit reached)
  
- **Analytics**: Visual charts, professional metrics explained, comparison features
  - Traders understand performance and can improve strategies intelligently

### 5.3 Advanced features & edge cases

- **Strategy versioning**: Save parameter history, compare backtest results across versions
- **Broker failover**: If primary broker offline, queue orders for retry
- **Network error handling**: Graceful degradation, sync data when connection restored
- **Duplicate order prevention**: Idempotency keys prevent accidental re-execution
- **Manual override**: Trader can close position manually if strategy stuck
- **Data gaps**: Alert if backtest period has missing data, suggest alternative dates
- **Slippage simulation**: Model realistic execution prices, not just close prices
- **Performance under load**: System handles 1000+ concurrent traders, 10K trades/minute

### 5.4 UI/UX highlights

- **Dark theme** (professional trading aesthetic, reduces eye strain)
- **Real-time updates** via WebSocket (no page refresh needed)
- **Mobile-responsive** (90% feature parity on mobile)
- **Keyboard shortcuts** (advanced traders love shortcuts)
- **Dark charts** (TradingView-style candlestick charts)
- **One-click actions** (deploy, pause, close, are all single clicks)
- **Inline explanations** (hover for definitions of Sharpe ratio, drawdown, etc.)
- **Error messages** (clear, actionable, suggest solutions)

